title: Mumbai-Spiced Chicken & Carrot Ribbon Salad with Garlic Yoghurt & Coriander
description: It’s good to relax and refresh, and a good meal can be the first step! Our Mumbai spice blend adds mild and fragrant flavours to delicate chicken. Served on a bed of crunchy carrot salad, this meal is sure to rejuvenate you at the end of a long day.

